title: Triple J (JJJ) Hottest 100 of 2007 (fixed)
description:
The Hottest Songs of 2007 as voted in Australia&#039;s biggest publicly voted music countdown. Run by Triple J (JJJ).

This is a resubmission of http://thepiratebay.se/tor/3998437/ which has 2 incorrect Foo Fighters songs. Namely Track 6 and 82 should have been &#039;The Pretender&#039; and &#039;Long Road to Ruin&#039; but were instead &#039;Once and For All&#039; and &#039;Statues&#039; respectively. These have both been corrected in this torrent, thanks to marcus_ivo for pointing it out.

All tracks except the 2 that were replaced are identical to http://thepiratebay.se/tor/3998437/ for those willing and able to redirect their torrent software.

File sizes have been optimised to minimise file sizes and maximise quality using Variable Bitrate Encoding (alt-preset-standard). The majority of original files were 320kbps. All leading and trailing silences have been removed. All track volumes have been normalized to 100%.

The track listing includes a bonus track from Melbourne band Reckless Enemy&#039;s latest album, Shady Characters.

Enjoy.
